    "client_msg_id": "F0E92B93-ACBC-4793-8112-3D9F84038EF8",
    "text": "It sounds like the goal quote was found, but I want to share a related one from the Malofiej journalism conference in 2016\n\n>> ““If you make a tooltip or rollover, assume no one will ever see it.”\n>> \n> 85% of page visitors simply ignore them, missing out on information hidden behind interaction.”\nFrom Archie Tse (NYT graphics editor) on why the Times was doing fewer interactives \n\n<https://github.com/archietse/malofiej-2016/blob/master/tse-malofiej-2016-slides.pdf|https://github.com/archietse/malofiej-2016/blob/master/tse-malofiej-2016-slides.pdf>",
